# Convergence wrapper for ISTHMUS marching-grid resolution on a sphere.

units si

variable refinement equal 20
variable mcres equal 1
variable steps equal 5

voxel_material carbon density 1800.0
voxel_create solid sphere diameter 1.0e-3 resolution 12 material carbon

source q1 constant 0.8 units kg/m2/s
timestep mass/courant 0.5 source q1

stats 1000000
stats_style step time active-voxels deleted-voxels remaining-mass mass-fraction volume-fraction radius

variable i loop ${steps}
label ablate-loop
isthmus_surf skin voxels solid buffer ${mcres} resolution ${mcres}:1 weighting no map yes
surf_flux skin source q1 select all
voxel_ablate solid surface skin policy carryover/normal delete yes
run 1
next i
jump SELF ablate-loop

convergence radius exact "initial-radius - q1*time/rho" tolerance 100.0 percent norm final vary refinement 1 2 10 vary mcres 10 5 1 vary steps 5 5 5 order 0.2 3.0 monotonic no
